{
  "id": "adv_card_hrk_07_01",
  "title": "佐伯遙子 1話 むちっとはしてるけど",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_toffice_evening",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "――という感じで、雫ちゃんに誘ってもらった\nアイドルのライブが最高だったの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "―― So‚ Shizuku-chan invited me to an idol live‚ and it was amazing!\nand it was amazing!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "いい刺激になったんですね、良かったです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's great to hear. I'm glad it had a positive impact on you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.9823582966,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "そうそう！　私ももっともーっと頑張ろうって思えたの\n佐伯遙子、また明日からがんがん行くわよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Exactly! I feel even more motivated now.\nHaruko Saeki is going to work even harder from tomorrow onwards!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "あ、いけない。そろそろスーパーに行かないと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ wait. I need to go to the supermarket soon.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.3451750755,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "買い出しなら手伝いましょうか？\n俺も今日の仕事はもう終わりなので",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Need any help with the shopping?\nSince my work for today is done.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "え？　そんな、悪いわよ……と言いたいけど\nせっかくなら厚意に甘えちゃおうかな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? You sure? I feel bad about it‚ but if you insist…\nI might as well take advantage of your offer then.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01-hrk005.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうね、付き合ってもらって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thanks for coming along.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.6833836238,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "どういたしまして。……それにしても\n最近よく遙子さんが買い出しに行ってませんか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're welcome‚ but…\nhave you been going shopping quite often lately?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01-hrk006.m4a",
      "text": "今のサニピってもの凄く忙しいでしょ？\nそれに私以外は高校生で、沢山予定が詰まってるし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sunny Peace is really busy these days‚ you know?\nAnd besides‚ everyone else is still in high school with packed schedules.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.9212495343,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01-hrk007.m4a",
      "text": "だからみんなの負担を少しでも減らそうと思って\n料理当番を積極的に買って出てるってわけ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ I thought I'd try to lighten their load a bit\nby taking on cooking duties actively.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.2447529475,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "その心遣いはとてもありがたいですけど\n遙子さんだって大学が忙しいんじゃないですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Your thoughtfulness is much appreciated‚\nbut aren't you busy with college too‚ Haruko-san?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01-hrk008.m4a",
      "text": "私はほら、アイドルのお仕事があんまりない時に\n単位を取りまくっちゃったから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ you see‚ I managed to pile up credits\nduring the slow periods of idol work‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01-hrk009.m4a",
      "text": "なんていうか、結構融通が利くのよ\nあくまで多少ね？　多少だから！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "so I have some flexibility.\nIt's just a little bit‚ okay? Just a little!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "あー……なんというかその、すみません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah… I see. Um‚ sorry about that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.9760926882,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01-hrk010.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっと、もう。そんな真剣に謝らなくっていいってば\nそれじゃあ、そろそろ行こっか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ cut it out. No need to apologize so seriously.\nWell then‚ shall we get going?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistore-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistore-00-noon",
      "startTime": 101.5203536987
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistore-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistore-00-noon",
      "startTime": 101.5203536987
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 102
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01-hrk011.m4a",
      "text": "う～ん、お惣菜コーナーから試食のいい匂いが……\n衝動買いしないように気を付けないと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm‚ the smell of the sample tasting from the deli section…\nI need to be careful not to give in to impulse buying.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっとくらい買ってもいいんじゃないですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Maybe it's okay to buy a little bit?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.2465587298,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistore-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistore-00-noon",
      "startTime": 114.9731420357
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01-hrk012.m4a",
      "text": "ダメよ！　ちょっと油断して食べる物を\n増やそうものなら……大変なことになるんだから！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No way! If I start adding\nmore tempting foods even a little bit… it'll be trouble!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.7999913533,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistore-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistore-00-noon",
      "startTime": 121.4889012495
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01-hrk013.m4a",
      "text": "この間だって、お仕事の差し入れでもらったケーキを\n食べてたら、怜ちゃんに凄い顔されたの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The other day‚ when I was eating a cake someone brought\nas a work treat… Rei-chan gave me this serious look and said‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.9999913533,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01-hrk014.m4a",
      "text": "「衣装が入らなくなっちゃいますよ？」……なんて\n爆弾を落とされたんだから！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "\"Your costumes won't fit anymore‚ you know?\"\n… It was like dropping a bomb!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.2801659449,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistore-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistore-00-noon",
      "startTime": 134.6826200643
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01-hrk015.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫だもん、気を付けてるから……むちっとしてても\n体重は増えてないし……むちっとはしてるけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But it's okay‚ I'm being careful…\neven though I might be chubby a bit…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.3263275057,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistore-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistore-00-noon",
      "startTime": 146.0318715571
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "そ、それは失礼しました……\nまさかそこまでシビアだとは",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-I'm sorry for that…\nI didn't realize it was that strict.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.76665802,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistore-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistore-00-noon",
      "startTime": 151.1557256061
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01-hrk016.m4a",
      "text": "そういう訳だから、女の子に軽率に\n誘惑を持ち掛けないように！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's why you shouldn't tempt girls\nso recklessly!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154.4333246867,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistore-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistore-00-noon",
      "startTime": 158.7117777824
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01-hrk017.m4a",
      "text": "ハッ！　お菓子の特売……！？\nだ、ダメよ、負けちゃダメ、遙子……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh?! Special sale on snacks…!?\nNo‚ no‚ I can't give in. Stay strong‚ Haruko…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 162.4999913533,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "（ほ、本当に大変なんだな……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Wow… it seems really tough…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 166.916403834,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistore-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistore-00-noon",
      "startTime": 171.1676156521
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01-hrk018.m4a",
      "text": "えーっと、野菜はこれくらいでいいかな\n次はお肉ね。今日は確か鶏肉が安くなってたから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let's see… I think this much vegetables is enough.\nNext is meat. I remember chicken being on sale today…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 176.5333246867,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
